item.title: Help plz rep++
item.dc:creator: @Project_Realm Project Realm
item.description:
@Project_Realm wrote:

You possibly placed your cache in the wrong directory. Try putting it in a directory named “cache614” within your main hard drive (for instance, C:). So, your cache should all be within the directory with the full file name of “C:/cache614/”. That’s how my client is configured.
